analysis_result.summary: The rental agreement covers Flat No. 302, Rose Residency, Baner, Pune, owned by Mr. Rajesh Sharma and rented to Ms. Priya Nair, a software engineer at Infosys Pune. The monthly rent is ₹25,000, with a ₹2,000 maintenance charge. The security deposit is ₹75,000, paid via cheque no. 128756. The 11-month tenancy starts on 01/03/2025 and ends on 31/01/2026. The agreement is signed by Ms. Nair, Mr. Sharma, and witnesses Mr. Sanjay Kulkarni and Mrs. Ritu Deshmukh.
